snippet.title: Hacker Evolution Untold Trailer Small
snippet.description:
Official trailer for the newly released game:
Hacker Evolution: Untold

More details on: http://www.exosyphen.com/page_hacker-evolution-untold.html

Description:
When the first technological singularity is encountered, and the world is about to collapse, you find yourself framed for a crime that you haven't comit.
Use your hacker skills to prevent computers from becoming the next dominant specie on the planet, and clear your name.
And there is more to it, than that...
